#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid "Woob Importer"
msgstr "Uvoznik Woob"

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "What is Woob?"
msgstr "Kaj je Woob?"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://woob.tech/\">Woob</ulink></acronym>, or "
"<quote>Web outside of browsers</quote> is <quote>a collection of "
"applications able to interact with websites, without requiring the user to "
"open them in a browser.</quote> One of <ulink url=\"https://woob.tech/"
"applications/\">such applications</ulink> allows specifically to interact "
"with <ulink url=\"https://woob.tech/applications/bank\">financial "
"institutions</ulink>. &kmymoney; provides a plugin that employs it directly, "
"therefore allowing to import transactions from those banks and institutions "
"which otherwise do not offer support for any other financial protocol that "
"&kmymoney; handles."
msgstr ""
"<acronym><ulink url=\"https://woob.tech/\">Woob</ulink></acronym> ali "
"<quote>Splet zunaj brskalnikov</quote> je <quote>zbirka aplikacij, ki lahko "
"interakcijo s spletnimi mesti, ne da bi jih uporabnik moral odpreti v "
"brskalniku.</quote> Ena od <ulink url=\"https://woob.tech/applications/"
"\">takih aplikacij</ulink> omogoča posebej komunicirajte s <ulink url="
"\"https://woob.tech/applications/bank\">finančnimi institucijami</ulink>. "
"&kmymoney; ponuja vtičnik, ki ga neposredno uporablja, kar omogoča uvoz "
"transakcij iz tistih bank in ustanov, ki sicer ne ponujajo podpore za noben "
"drug finančni protokol, ki ga obdeluje &kmymoney;."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installing Woob"
msgstr "Namestitev Woob"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmymoney; currently requires that you install Woob independently. See below "
"for details."
msgstr ""
"&kmymoney; trenutno zahteva, da Woob namestite neodvisno. Za podrobnosti "
"glejte spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some &Linux; distributions package Woob, and that is the preferred method of "
"installation, if it is available. If not, you need to install a recent "
"version of Python 3 first before continuing. All major &Linux; distributions "
"package Python, and you should use that version, if possible. Otherwise, you "
"can download a package for your system from the <ulink url=\"https://www."
"python.org/downloads/\">official Python website</ulink>. The exact minimum "
"version of Python required by Woob can be found on the <ulink url=\"https://"
"woob.tech/install/\">Woob website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere &Linux; distribucije pakirajo Woob, in to je najprimernejši način "
"namestitve, če je na voljo. Če ne, morate najprej namestiti najnovejšo "
"različico Python 3, preden nadaljujete. Vsi glavni &Linux;i distribuirajo "
"paket Python in uporabite to različico, če je mogoče. V nasprotnem primeru "
"lahko prenesete paket za svoj sistem z <ulink url=\"https://www.python.org/"
"downloads/\">uradne spletne strani Python</ulink>. Natančno najmanjšo "
"različico Pythona, ki jo zahteva Woob, lahko najdete na <ulink url=\"https://"
"woob.tech/install/\">spletnem mestu Woob</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With Python 3 installed, you should now be able to easily download and "
"install the required Woob modules. Please refer to the instructions on the "
"Woob website. When &kmymoney; runs, it checks for the presence of Woob, and "
"loads the plugin if Woob is found. See the <link linkend=\"details.settings."
"plugins\">Plugins</link> section in the <link linkend=\"details.settings"
"\">Settings</link> chapter for more information on confirming that the woob "
"plugin is loaded."
msgstr ""
"Z nameščenim Pythonom 3 bi zdaj morali imeti možnost enostavno prenesti in "
"namestiti zahtevane module Woob. Oglejte si navodila na spletnem mestu Woob. "
"Ko &kmymoney; zažene, preveri prisotnost Wooba in naloži vtičnik, če Woob "
"najde. Glejte razdelek <link linkend=\"details.settings.plugins\">Vtičniki</"
"link> v poglavju <link linkend=\"details.settings\">Nastavitve</link> za več "
"informacij o potrditvi, da je vtičnik woob naložen."

#. Tag: title
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Woob"
msgstr "Uporaba Woob"

#. Tag: para
#: details-impexp-woob.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If Woob is installed, and the &kmymoney; woob plugin is loaded, you should "
"be able to set it up for use with an account by invoking the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Map to online account...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu item. Once that is done, the <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Account</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Update account...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> menu item will download transactions for that account using Woob."
msgstr ""
"Če je Woob nameščen in &kmymoney; je vtičnik woob naložen, bi ga morali "
"imeti možnost nastaviti za uporabo z računom s klicem <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Preslikava v spletni račun ...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> element menija. Ko je to storjeno, bo menijski "
"element <menuchoice> <guimenu>Račun</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Posodobi račun ..."
"</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> prenesel transakcije za ta račun z uporabo Woob."

